snippet.title: FrankenStorm TD Steam Coming Soon Trailer
snippet.description:
Big news! The first milestone for the full version of FrankenStorm TD has been reached: Steam Coming Soon page is up with our first trailer!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1857390/FrankenStorm_TD/

Special thanks to Tim Duncan for his great work on our trailer! You can see more of his work @timduncanproductions
